---
import Layout from "../layouts/Main.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="about us | mmnc" description="meow!">
    <Header class="bg-about bg-center bg-cover h-96 flex flex-col" />
    <main class="mx-auto mt-12 px-8 max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="text-center pb-8">about us</h1>
        <p>hey there, first off, thanks for reading up on us.</p>

        <p>
            our server always runs the latest version of minecraft, but we plan
            to also include a b1.7.3 flavor of mmnc as a seperate server in the
            near future :3
            <br />
            head to the home screen to get the IP to join us!
        </p>

        <p>
            we also intend to open source everything - our plugins, this website
            and more - all on our github
        </p>

        <h2>How to play?</h2>
        <p>
            our IP is on the home page of this website, <a href="/"
                >so go there and copy it :3</a
            >
        </p>
        <p>
            we recommend the <a
                href="https://modrinth.com/modpack/fabulously-optimized"
                >Fabulously Optimized modpack</a
            >, which you can download immediately from inside <a
                href="https://prismlauncher.org/">Prism Launcher</a
            >
        </p>
        <p>
            additionally, to spice up your experience, you can use the <a
                href="https://modrinth.com/plugin/simple-voice-chat"
                >Simple Voice Chat mod</a
            > (optional), which our server supports c:
        </p>

        <h2>Code of Conduct <br /> (Da Rules)</h2>
        <p>
            it's important that we, the players, don't flip our little cute
            server on it's head. so we prepared some rules that you'll have to
            follow if you want to play:
        </p>
        <ol class="mb-8 list-decimal">
            <li>No exploits, hacking/cheating or griefing</li>
            <li>No homophobia, transphobia, xenophobia, racism etc.</li>
            <li>Don't be a mean kitty/ouppy</li>
            <li>
                Use CWs when you can, so people aren't put off by stuff you say
                or build
            </li>
            <li>No doxxing, harassment, ban evasion or dogpiling</li>
            <li>
                Do not spread false or misleading information and/or malicious
                links
            </li>
            <li>Do not promote violent ideologies or incite violence</li>
        </ol>

        <h2>The fun stuff</h2>
        <p>our server features:</p>
        <ul class="mb-8 list-disc">
            <li>
                Enhanced vanilla survival experience, no pay2win stuff or extra
                mechanics
            </li>
            <li>
                The ability to set your real height with <code
                    >/height [your height in cm]</code
                >
            </li>
            <li>
                Pronouns with <a href="https://pronoundb.org/">PronounDB.org</a>
                integration
            </li>
            <li>
                Emojis! Simply use <code>:emoji:</code>, for e.g. <code
                    >:star:</code
                > to print a ‚≠ê
            </li>
            <li>
                Voice chat support through <a
                    href="https://modrinth.com/plugin/simple-voice-chat"
                    >Simple Voice Chat</a
                > mod
            </li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How to report bugs or players?</h2>
        <p>
            tell an admin (pink name) or mod (light blue name) in chat, or <a
                href="https://github.com/orgs/meowmeownyacraft/discussions"
                >tell us on github discussions</a
            >
        </p>
        <p>
            if it's a <strong>bug</strong>, then make a github issue <a
                href="https://github.com/meowmeownyacraft/mmnc/issues">here</a
            >
        </p>

        <h2>The cute cat girls (staff)</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>i1vy (she/her)</li>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="https://i1vy.moe/">Website</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://blahaj.zone/@i1vy">Fedi</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://namemc.com/profile/i1vy.2">NameMC</a></li>
            </ul>
            <li>nvkomata (she/her)</li>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="https://nvkomata.gitlab.io/">Website</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://akko.wtf/nvkomata">Fedi</a></li>
                <li>
                    <a href="https://namemc.com/profile/nvkomata.1">NameMC</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </ul>
    </main>
    <Footer />
</Layout>


<style>
    @tailwind base;
            @layer base {
                ul,
                ol,
                li {
                    list-style: revert-layer;
                    padding: revert-layer;
                }
            }

            h1,
            h2,
            h3,
            h4,
            h5,
            h6 {
                margin: 1.5rem 0;
                line-height: 1.2;
                font-weight: 800;
                font-family: monospace;
                text-transform: capitalize;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 2.752em;
            }
            h2 {
                font-size: 2.041em;
            }
            h3 {
                font-size: 1.953em;
            }
            h4 {
                font-size: 1.563em;
            }
            h5 {
                font-size: 1.25em;
            }
            strong,
            b {
                font-weight: 700;
            }
            a {
                color: #fbc6f6;
                transition: all 0.1 ease-out;
            }
            a:hover {
                color: #d88dd1;
            }
            p {
                margin-bottom: 1em;
            }
            .prose p {
                margin-bottom: 2em;
            }
            textarea {
                width: 100%;
                font-size: 16px;
            }
            input {
                font-size: 16px;
            }
            table {
                width: 100%;
            }
            img {
                max-width: 100%;
                height: auto;
                border-radius: 8px;
            }
            code {
                padding: 2px 5px;
                background-color: #5252524c;
                border-radius: 2px;
            }
            pre {
                padding: 1.5em;
                border-radius: 8px;
            }
            pre > code {
                all: unset;
            }
            blockquote {
                border-left: 4px solid #63636395;
                padding: 0 0 0 20px;
                margin: 0px;
                font-size: 1.333em;
            }
            hr {
                border: none;
                border-top: 1px solid #63636395;
            }
            @media (max-width: 720px) {
                body {
                    font-size: 18px;
                }
            }

            .sr-only {
                border: 0;
                padding: 0;
                margin: 0;
                position: absolute;
                height: 1px;
                width: 1px;
                overflow: hidden;
                clip-path: inset(50%);
                white-space: nowrap;
            }

            ul,
            ol {
                margin-bottom: 2em;
                margin-top: 2em;
            }
            ul ol,
            ol ol,
            ul ul,
            ol ul {
                margin-bottom: 0.5em;
                margin-top: 0.5em;
            }
    
    </style>
    